        <td valign="top"> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- SLMA SUCCESSFULLY CONDUCTS THE GAMES NIGHT OF 1ST HALF – 2015 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 14/02/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>The Games Night Organized by the officer cadets of Intakes 80, 81, 81A, 82, 54A(V) and 55(V) at the Sri Lanka Military Academy (SLMA), Diyatalawa on Saturday 14th February 2015 gave the guest an opportunity to have fun and enjoyment until the midnight.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=350">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/games_night1half2015/9.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- SPORT MEET &nbsp;- 2015 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7/02/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>The Biannual Inter Company Sports Meet of the Sri Lanka Military Academy was held on Saturday 7th February 2015 at the Polo Ground,</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=349">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/sport_meet_2015_1st/4.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- ADMIN INSPECTION - 2015 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6/02/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>The Chief of Staff of the Sri Lanka Army, Major General S A P P Samarasinghe and Directors and respective subject officers of all branches and directorates arrived at the Academy on 6 February 2015 for the annual admin inspection.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=347">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/cos_visit_2015/3.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- 19TH COMMANDING OFFICER OF THE OFFICER CADET WING &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2/02/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>Col SRB Aluvihare RWP RSP psc took over duties as the 19th Commanding Officer of the Officer Cadet Wing on 02nd February 2015 from the outgoing Commanding Officer Col JMC Jayaweera psc.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=346">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/co_taking_over/3.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- ANNUAL FAREWELL - 2014 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 31/01/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>The annual farewell of the Sri Lanka Military Academy was held on 31st January 2015 at the Officers’ Mess to bid farewell to the officers who relinquished their duties during the year 2014.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=345">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/farewel_2014/1.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- THE EXERCISE FROZEN TROUT &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 31/01/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>Eighty-five Officer Cadets from Intake 81, 54 A (V), Lady 13A and 55 (V) participated in the Ex FROZEN TROUT conducted at Ambewela and Pattipola area from 26 January to 31 January 2015.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=351">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/ex frozen trout2015 1half/6.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- INDIAN DEFENCE ADVISOR MEETS THE COMMANDANT &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 21/01/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>The Defence Advisor to Indian High Commission in Colombo Captain Prakash Gopalan made a courtesy call on the Commandant of Sri Lanka Military Academy (SLMA), Diyatalawa, Brigadier RWWADB Rajaguru at his office on Wednesday (21 January 2015).</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=344">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img width="354" height="236" src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2015/INDIAN DEFENCE ADVISOR VIST 2015/2.JPG"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- A DELEGATION FROM THE INDIAN MILITARY ACADEMY &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 07/01/2015 </span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>A delegation from the Indian military Academy, India comprising of an Officer Instructor and three Gentleman Cadets visited the Sri Lanka Military Academy on 07 January 2015 as part of an exchange programme.</p> <p style="text-align: justify