="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em;">--- PASSING OUT OFFICER CADETS PROVE THEIR METTLE TO THE COMMANDANT OF THEIR ALMA- MATER &nbsp; &nbsp; 18/06/2014</span></p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong> </strong> </span>Officers Cadets of passing out Intakes 78, 53A and Lady 12A at the Sri Lanka Military Academy (SLMA) , Diyatalawa proved their mettle to the Commandant SLMA Brigadier I P Ranasinghe, at the Commandant’s Parade on Wednesday (18) morning at the Academy Parade Square. This colourful parade consisting of 2 Officers, 8 Senior Non Commission Officers (SNCOs) and 183 Officer Cadets including 60 passing out Officer Cadets with one Lady Officer Cadet was commenced precisely at 9.00 a.m with the arrival of the Commandant SLMA.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/slma_joomla/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=281">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></p> <p><img src="/slma_joomla/images/news/2014/pop_comdparad_2014/10.JPG" height="235" width="354"></p> <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p> </td> 
